        <div class="faq-grid">
          <div class="faq-col">
            <div class="faq-item fade-up"><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false"><span>How much does security camera installation cost?</span><span class="faq-icon"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M6 2v8M2 6h8"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-answer"><p>Installation pricing depends on the number of cameras, camera type, wiring requirements, and roof/height access needed. We provide flat-rate quotes upfront. A single doorbell camera installation differs significantly from a 4-camera wired outdoor system — both have transparent pricing.</p></div></div>
